---
import WidgetLayout from '../../layouts/WidgetLayout.astro';
---
<WidgetLayout title="TextArea">
  <h1>TextArea</h1>
  <p>Multi-line text input with scroll.</p>

  <h2>Preview</h2>
  <pre class="ascii-mockup">┌────────────────────────────────┐   <span class="focused">╭────────────────────────────────╮</span>   <span class="focused">╭────────────────────────────────╮</span>
│Turn 3: Flanked the left side   │   <span class="focused">│</span>Turn 3: Flanked the left side   <span class="focused">│</span>   <span class="focused">│</span>with terminators. Enemy lost  ▲ <span class="focused">│</span>
│with terminators. Enemy lost    │   <span class="focused">│</span>with terminators. Enemy lost    <span class="focused">│</span>   <span class="focused">│</span>2 units.                        <span class="focused">│</span>
│2 units.                        │   <span class="focused">│</span>2 units.█                       <span class="focused">│</span>   <span class="focused">│</span>                                <span class="focused">│</span>
│                                │   <span class="focused">│</span>                                <span class="focused">│</span>   <span class="focused">│</span>Deployed reserves on turn 4.  ▼ <span class="focused">│</span>
└────────────────────────────────┘   <span class="focused">╰────────────────────────────────╯</span>   <span class="focused">╰────────────────────────────────╯</span>
 unfocused                            focused (cursor visible)              scrolled</pre>

  <h2>Accessible mode</h2>
  <p><code>Notes: Turn 3: Flanked the left side with terminators. Enemy lost 2 units.</code></p>

  <h2>Props</h2>
  <table>
    <thead><tr><th>Prop</th><th>Type</th><th>Notes</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>value</td><td>string</td><td></td></tr>
      <tr><td>onChange</td><td>function</td><td></td></tr>
      <tr><td>width</td><td>number</td><td></td></tr>
      <tr><td>height</td><td>number</td><td></td></tr>
      <tr><td>placeholder</td><td>string?</td><td></td></tr>
      <tr><td>wrap</td><td>boolean?</td><td>default true</td></tr>
      <tr><td>readOnly</td><td>boolean?</td><td></td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2>Usage</h2>
  <pre><code>&lt;TextArea value={'{'}notes{'}'} onChange={'{'}setNotes{'}'} width={'{'}40{'}'} height={'{'}5{'}'} /&gt;</code></pre>

  <h2>Interactive demo</h2>
  <div class="demo-placeholder">Interactive demo coming soon</div>
</WidgetLayout>
